About Me

My name is Greg Rousis and I am a 3rd year graduate student in the social psychology program at USF. This page will be used as a homework repository for Programming With Data. I work in the Gender and Interpersonal Dynamics Lab GID Lab with Jennifer Bosson and Joe Vandello.

My research interests include:

1. Online extremism

2. Sexism

3. Manhood and masculinity
